This paper is related to the design and optimization of communication networks, specifically cloud radio access networks (C-RANs) which are a type of wireless access network. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization techniques and mathematical programming, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper deals with the management of mobile data traffic, which could place it in the category of cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
